						<figure><a href="/cnt/ntnl-scrt/cntr-trrrsm/pssngr-prtct/cndn-trvl-nmbr/index-en.aspx?utm_source=ps-web&utm_medium=ps-features&utm_campaign=ps-sp-passenger-protec-20-21" data-gc-analytics="promo:homePageFeature">
							<figcaption>
								<h3 id="feature4e" class="h5">Canadian Travel Number (CTN)</h3>
							</figcaption>
							<img src="cnt\_mgs\cmpgns\cndn-trvl-nmbr-wb-ftr-bil.jpg" alt="Canadian Travel Number (CTN)" class="img-responsive mrgn-bttm-sm hidden-sm hidden-xs" /> </a> </figure>
						<p>A CTN prevents delays at the airport for travellers who have the same, or similar, name as someone on the Secure Air Travel Act (SATA) list.</p>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Feature 5 -->
					
					<div class="col-md-4">
